
{center}
{subhead} Tornado3D v2.0 SE{def}
{left}
{p} {p}

FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE{p}
Tornado3D v2.0 SE{p}
{p} {p}
This special version of Tornado3D has all you need to create breath-taking
3D graphics and animation at a very reasonable price and with a full
upgrade option.  Includes PowerPC and Virge3D support.  You can get this
outstanding 3D package for only 199 DM.  Just some of Tornado3D 2.0 SE's
features are:
{p} {p}
	Volumetric Lights{p}
	PowerPC rendering with separate specially-optimized 603e and 604e modules{p}
	Real-time 3D color shaded preview{p}
	Real-time interactive rendering{p}
	Virge3D support{p}
	Splines{p}
	Deformation Cages{p}
	Automorphing{p}
	Projector Lights{p}
	Clipmapped Shadows{p}
	Selective Raytracing for Reflections, Refractions and Shadows{p}
	Cubic Reflections and Refractions{p}
	Additive and normal transparency{p}
	Pose Manager{p}
	Lens Flares{p}
	Postscript(tm) font import{p}
	Lightwave objects import{p}
	DXF import and export{p}
	Imagine objects and groups import{p}
	Metameshing with selectable Edge Tension{p}
	Procedural Textures plug-ins{p}
	Multiple Shaders (Matte, Dull, Plastic, Metal, Glass){p}
	Unlimited maps and textures per surface{p}
	Turbulent and quiet 3D fog{p}
	Linear, Early, Late quadratic and user fog kinds{p}
	Distant, Point, Spot and Umbrella light sources{p}
	Animatable Volumetric Hypertextures{p}
	Extrusion, lathing, replication and arraying{p}
	Spline skinning{p}
	Nurbs polygonization{p}
	Interactive animation panel{p}
	Interactive Move, Scale, Rotate, Bend, Taper, Twist, Shear, Mould and Pinch{p}
	Inverse Kinematics{p}
	Interpolated Shading{p}
	Soft Shadows{p}
	High quality shadow maps and clipmapped shadows for rotoscoping{p}
	Subdivide, fractalize, triangulate, Normalize, Refine{p}
	Displacement mapping{p}
	Image creation panel{p}
	Full graphics card support{p}
	Datatype V43 support{p}
	IFF, TGA, JPEG and RAW internal loaders and savers{p}
	...and much more
{p} {p}
